.TH "HERMES" "1" "June 2026" "hermes User Manuals" "Version 0.7.1"
.hy
.SH NAME
.PP
hermes - graphical manager for product warranties
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\f[B]hermes\f[R]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
\f[B]hermes\f[R] is a free and open-source Qt5 graphical application to
manage your products\[cq] warranties.
It allows you to:
.IP \[bu] 2
add products with their purchase date and warranty end date,
.IP \[bu] 2
attach invoice and warranty certificate documents to each product,
.IP \[bu] 2
mark products currently in after-sales service (SAV),
.IP \[bu] 2
search through your product list,
.IP \[bu] 2
configure the data storage location.
.PP
Product data is stored locally in \f[B]\[ti]/deuchnord-hermes/\f[R] in
both a legacy binary format (\f[I].hrms\f[R]) and individual JSON files
for future compatibility.
.PP
Hermes checks for new upstream versions at startup and notifies the user
in the status bar when one is available.
.SH FILES
.TP
\f[I]\[ti]/deuchnord-hermes/products.hrms\f[R]
Main product database (legacy binary format, Qt5 QDataStream).
.TP
\f[I]\[ti]/deuchnord-hermes/json/*.json\f[R]
Per-product JSON files (format used by future versions).
.SH BUGS
.PP
Report bugs at
<https://tickets.deuchnord.fr/index.php?project=2&do=index&switch=1>.
.SH SEE ALSO
.PP
Online documentation: <https://doc.deuchnord.fr/hermes/start>
